name: Kanto Eeveelutions
description: Jolteon, Vaporeon and Flareon are the original Eeveelutions that were introduced in the Generation I Pokémon games (Pokémon Red/Blue). Eeveelution is a term used for the current group of eight Pokémon that evolve from Eevee. It is a portmanteau of the words "Eevee" and "evolution".
